qProperty.markdown:
^[%[The **Answers Analyzer** is an application designed for Qlik Cloud to track and analyze Qlik Answers related content within a tenant. Some of the benefits of this application are as follows:](4)](inherit)^[%[
](4)](inherit)^[%[**\- Track user questions across knowledgebases, assistants, and source documents**](3)](inherit)^[%[**\- Analyze user behavior to see what types of questions users are asking about what content**](3)](inherit)^[%[**\- Optimize knowledgebase sizes and increase answer accuracy by removing inaccurate, unused, and unreferenced documents**](3)](inherit)^[%[**\- Track and monitor page size to quota**](3)](inherit)^[%[**\- Ensure that data is kept up to date by monitoring knowledgebase index times**](3)](inherit)^[%[**\- Tie alerts into metrics, \(e.g. a knowledgebase hasn't been updated in over X days\)**](3)](inherit)^[%[**
**](3)](inherit)^[^[**As of this application's initial release, it does not have the ability to:**](inherit)^[\- Access certain content within users' Personal spaces. I.e., it does not have visibility to the specific questions asked, specific answers provided, or individual metadata for knowledgebase documents that reside there. This is a current API limitation.](inherit)](inherit)^[**%[_
_](2)**](inherit)^[**%[Endpoints:](3)**](inherit)^[^[^[tenants \- public](inherit)^[licenses/overview \- public](inherit)^[users \- public](inherit)^[spaces \- public](inherit)^[data\-connections \- public](inherit)^[knowledgebases \- private](inherit)^[knowledgebases/<id> \- private](inherit)^[knowledgebases/<id>/datasources/<id>/documents \- private](inherit)^[assistants \- private](inherit)^[assistants/<id>/threads \- private](inherit)^[assistants/<id>/threads/<id> \- private](inherit)](inherit)](inherit)

extensionMeta.name: Layout container
extensionMeta.description: The layout container object has a canvas that can hold multiple objects. In this container you can freely move objects around, as well as position the objects on top of each other or overlapping.
